Brief:

Simple program to copy a file on local filesystems with a limited rate.
Useful if you have a slow bus and need to safe qos/disk latency.

Syntax:

  java org.gnu.dc.Program <INFILE> <OUTFILE> <MB/s>

Example:

  java org.gnu.dc.Program file-a /tmp/file-a 8

Copies "file-a" to "/tmp" and let's you still work, if your disks are
connected via your usb2 hub.
